.main-content
  .jumbotron
    .container
      %h1 {{ site.title }}

      .row
        .col-sm-8
          %p Empower your Zendesk Help Center with Algolia Search and provide your users a Google-like search experience.

      .spacer50
      %p.text-center
        %a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg{href: 'mailto:hey@algolia.com?subject=Join%20the%20Zendesk%20beta'}
          Join the beta
          %i.fa.fa-envelope-o

  .container
    .spacer50
    %p.line-2x This JavaScript library allows you to replace the default search of your Zendesk Help Center by Algolia. Algolia is a hosted full-text, numerical, and faceted search engine capable of delivering realtime results from the first keystroke.
    %p.line-2x We'll crawl your Zendesk API to extract your Help Center content and provide you a small code snippet to power your search with Algolia.

    .spacer100
    %h1.headline Features
    .features
      .row
        .col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-3
          %h3 Auto-suggestions menu
          %p Offer End-Users immediate access to your whole help center from the dropdown menu, whatever your number of sections or articles.
        .col-sm-2.hidden-xs
          %img.img-responsive{src: 'http://placehold.it/200x200'}
      .row
        .col-sm-2.col-sm-offset-3.hidden-xs
          %img.img-responsive{src: 'http://placehold.it/200x200'}
        .col-sm-4
          %h3 Instant & Faceted Search
          %p Have your search results page, navigation and pagination updated in realtime, after each keystroke.
      .row
        .col-sm-4.col-sm-offset-3
          %h3 Relevance
          %p Increase customer satisfaction by serving relevant results.
        .col-sm-2.hidden-xs
          %img.img-responsive{src: 'http://placehold.it/200x200'}
      .row
        .col-sm-2.col-sm-offset-3.hidden-xs
          %img.img-responsive{src: 'http://placehold.it/200x200'}
        .col-sm-4
          %h3 Customizable
          %p Our code is open-source and hosted on GitHub, feel free to customize it.

